Package: tlp-rdw
Architecture: amd64
Description: Radio device wizard
 Radio device wizard is an add-on to TLP. It provides event based
 switching of bluetooth, NFC, Wi-Fi and WWAN radio devices on:
   - network connect/disconnect
   - dock/undock
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 network-manager,
 tlp,
